{"word":"Pharisees","slug":"pharisees","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Pharisees</b> A sect of the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=5'>Act 15:5</a><br/> Doctrines of:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=9'>Mat 15:9</a> <br/> - Concerning the resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=6'>Act 23:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=8'>Act 23:8</a> <br/> - Concerning association with publicans and sinners<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=13'>Mat 9:13</a> <br/> Traditions of:<br/> - Fasting<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=14'>Mat 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=12'>Luk 18:12</a> <br/> - The washing of hands<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=3'>Mat 15:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=15'>Mar 7:15</a> <br/> - The duties of children to parents<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=9'>Mat 15:9</a> <br/> - The Sabbath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=8'>Mat 12:8</a> <br/> Hypocrisy of:<br/> - Hypocrisy of:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=10'>Mat 3:10</a> <br/> - Reproved by Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=8'>Mat 6:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=18'>Mat 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=9'>Mat 15:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=12'>Mat 16:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=46'>Mat 21:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=23&verse=33'>Mat 23:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=54'>Luk 11:54</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=1'>Luk 12:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=15&verse=9'>Luk 15:9</a> <br/> Reject John<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=30'>Luk 7:30</a><br/> Reject Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=39'>Mat 12:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=12'>Mat 15:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=48'>Joh 7:48</a><br/> Come to Jesus with questions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=3'>Mat 19:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=22'>Mat 22:22</a><br/> Minister to Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=36'>Luk 7:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=37'>Luk 11:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=14&verse=1'>Luk 14:1</a><br/> Become disciples of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=1'>Joh 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=5'>Act 15:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22&verse=3'>Act 22:3</a><br/> Paul, a Pharisee<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=6'>Act 23:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=26&verse=5'>Act 26:5</a><br/><a href='S:Herodians'>Herodians</a>; <a href='S:Sadducees'>Sadducees</a>"}]}